Program: Outlook
Title: Festival of Devils
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbr01
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A look at La Endiablada, the centuries old 'Festival of Devils' in Spain. Also, the 'hellish' legacy of South Africa's collapsing coal mine in Witbank, and Les Nubians, the singing sisters who want their music to bridge the gap between Africa and Europe.